      purpose: Nonlinear AE baseline with raw input and misspecified isotropic MSE.
  03. ae_raw_mahalanobis | phase=ae_2x2 | model=small convolutional reconstruction AE | input=raw | loss=mahalanobis
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Separates loss geometry from input whitening: raw input, Mahalanobis loss.
  04. ae_prewhite_mse | phase=ae_2x2 | model=small convolutional reconstruction AE | input=prewhitened | loss=mse
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Tests whether prewhitened encoder input alone changes the learned solution.
  05. ae_prewhite_mahalanobis | phase=ae_2x2 | model=small convolutional reconstruction AE | input=prewhitened | loss=mahalanobis
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Geometry-first AE reference: prewhitened encoder input and Mahalanobis loss.
  06. transformer_raw_mse | phase=transformer_2x2 | model=token-preserving transformer reconstruction AE | input=raw | loss=mse
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Wrong metric / raw-token transformer baseline.
  07. transformer_raw_mahalanobis | phase=transformer_2x2 | model=token-preserving transformer reconstruction AE | input=raw | loss=mahalanobis
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Tests whether Mahalanobis loss helps without prewhitening attention input.
  08. transformer_prewhite_mse | phase=transformer_2x2 | model=token-preserving transformer reconstruction AE | input=prewhitened | loss=mse
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Tests attention on prewhitened tokens with isotropic native-output MSE.
  09. transformer_prewhite_mahalanobis | phase=transformer_2x2 | model=token-preserving transformer reconstruction AE | input=prewhitened | loss=mahalanobis
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Strongest current transformer config: prewhitened tokens and Mahalanobis loss.
  10. experiment_d_linear_prewhite_mahalanobis | phase=architecture | model=patch-linear reconstruction AE | input=prewhitened | loss=mahalanobis
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
      purpose: Fixed geometry architecture-bias baseline.
  11. experiment_d_cnn_prewhite_mahalanobis | phase=architecture | model=small convolutional reconstruction AE | input=prewhitened | loss=mahalanobis
      dataset: HDF5 detector traces from data.trace_path plus optional RQ labels from data.rq_path; PSD from preprocessing.psd_path.
